Game.....: Spawn: In The Demon's Hand
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: October 19th, 2000
Ripped.......: FMV Downsampled

The legendary hell-bound comic anti-hero comes to life on the Sega Dreamcast in Spawn. Straight from the blockbuster arcade game, this home version kicks it up a notch with even more features and modes of play.Up to 4 players can battle simultaneously in the "death match style" Team Battle Mode or choose a computer controlled teammate to take on Team Battle Tournament. All your favorite characters from the Spawn series are faithfully recreated in the ultimate death match challenge.